{"tid":1715693,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《守護年輕人》譴責警暴，促成立獨立調查聲明 聯署","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T07:11:54.000Z","uid":71111,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc34b3c89b6c66015eb5ceaa1b94ffebd258cc4","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScmXnE2QXnUDEKj3d9Q7B1AhHGUysFy4CKiFO_odo9bSLJq5w/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScmXnE2QXnUDEKj3d9Q7B1AhHGUysFy4CKiFO_odo9bSLJq5w%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=816af001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScmXnE2QXnUDEKj3d9Q7B1AhHGUysFy4CKiFO_odo9bSLJq5w/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n我們對警方於11月11日至13日凌晨時分處理社會示威事件的手法感到非常震驚，該等不合理、過份暴力及濫權的行為已超越執法的尺度。我們予以嚴厲譴責！ <br />\n<br />\n特區政府必須正視問題的根源，連串示威活動越演越烈，並不是因為治安失效，而是反映著香港人對於本屆政府和香港的未來感到無望和關切。因此，政府不能指派警方使用更大的武力以平息不滿，此舉只會令衝突不斷升溫。鑑於政府委任的國際專家小組成員Clifford Stott已表明警監會權力不足，我們強烈要求政府盡快成立獨立調查委員會，調查六月至今的警民衝突及市民對警方的一切投訴，以挽回市民對警隊的信心。<br />\n<br />\n作為香港的成年人，我們固然希望整個社會能處於平和安穩的氣氛中，但我們明白，原來的穩定與和諧，已埋下了今日危機的藥引。我們深愛下一代，他們是香港的未來，我們盡力保護年輕人，也願意以禱告守護年輕人，與他們同行，創造理想中的香港。希望年輕人確保自己及別人的安全，珍惜生命，懂得分辨所有為與不為。那怕別人說不可能，只要不屈不撓，存良知，香港才有希望。<br />\n<br />\n願我們所相信並倚靠的上帝垂念！<br />\n<br />\n一群愛香港下一代的成人聯署<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n有良知嘅教會，基督徒與香港人同行<br />\n請幫推上熱門，多d 人簽<br />\n守護學生，光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"c0adba8a39bc0a6ee59da49947a36872270dfaa0","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"3509aada999c695973554e05ba70df3840fe8277","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"292e06b7d230a9dca2e5836f57c666893399ad21","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"目前超過1500人簽咗"},{"pid":"c5fb5d195d40bd2555d32aa88939f1903c0cb991","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9819bc23a2ea07175ca3a9b03c752302fb9da74c","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f4f6ae076be5b797ac52e55f6ec9fbfb81972ae","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"清算近了"},{"pid":"76a303fd9e4eba2c33875061936d45b817bae0a0","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"解散警隊"},{"pid":"e1ac417727b9bfb5fd0e98443cc1a6c22d133e87","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"刻不容緩"},{"pid":"faab2e03cc4e27c12815a8557d59e1f1207eb35e","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"拒絕警暴"},{"pid":"fa769902a2892c709b21a6d10eb963fd9b59eed9","tid":1715693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"支持，已簽"},{"pid":"c8e72faedeb730631d69cb2443ce790727ecfe0e","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"3f812390720b8bde657b9854a597da0a410dea3f","tid":1715693,"uid":71111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"時代革命"}]}